prompts.frontCover: Minimalist greeting card front, flat 2D vector art. A humorous and lighthearted beach scene with a clean white background. In the lower half, a cartoon illustration of Lao Lao from the reference photo, with a big happy smile, is buried in the sand up to her neck. Only her head is visible, wearing a party hat jauntily on her head. The sand is represented by a simple, elegant tan shape. A few minimalist seashells and a small red sand crab are scattered on the sand near her. Standing beside the sand mound is a cartoon illustration of Jordan from the photo, wearing a sun hat and holding a small birthday cake with lit candles, grinning down at her. Jordan maintains his pose from the photo but is now presenting the cake. The art style is clean with simple lines and solid colors. Centered above the scene, the text "Happy Birthday Lao Lao!" is written in a beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script in a dark teal color.
